<p>When i click name in listbox(it is data from access i post only their name in listbox) and display all in textbox and edit anyhting (i.e name Prince to princeee) and click the button update i want also to update also in listbox . here's my code:</p>  <pre><code>Try         cn.Open()         With cmd             .Connection = cn             .CommandText = "UPDATE RegistrationTable set _Name ='" &amp; txtName.Text &amp; "',[_Age]='" &amp; txtAge.Text &amp; "',[_Gender]='" &amp; cmbGender.Text &amp; "',[_Phone]='" &amp; txtPhone.Text &amp; "',[_Address]='" &amp; txtAddress.Text &amp; "',[_Disease]='" &amp; txtDisease.Text &amp; "' where PatientID= '" &amp; txtPID.Text &amp; "'"             .ExecuteNonQuery()         End With         cn.Close()         ListBox1.Items.Clear()         cn.Open()         Dim Reader As OleDbDataReader         Dim query As String         query = "select * from RegistrationTable"         cmd = New OleDbCommand(query, cn)         Reader = cmd.ExecuteReader         While Reader.Read             Dim name = Reader("_Name")             ListBox1.Items.Add(name)         End While         cn.Close()          MsgBox("Update Success", MsgBoxStyle.Information)        Catch ex As Exception         MsgBox(ex.Message)     End Try  End Sub </code></pre>